<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُحالٌ الْكَذِبُ وَالمَنْهِىُّ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>كَعَدَمِ التَّبْلِيغِ يا ذَكِيُّ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>